== Other versions == 
* The first recording of the English-language version (lyrics by McKuen) was released on the 1963 album &quot;Time to Think&quot; by the Kingston Trio. 
* The Fortunes released a version of the song as a single in the UK in April 1969.
* The Beach Boys recorded a version of the song in 1971, which remained unreleased until the 2021 box set &quot;Feel Flows&quot; was released. 
* A cover version by Bobby Wright reached No. 24 on the &quot;Billboard&quot; Hot Country Singles chart in 1974.
* Nirvana recorded a version in 1993, which is the final recording on the &quot;With the Lights Out&quot; box set.
* Me First and the Gimme Gimmes recorded their version in 1997, featured on their album &quot;Have a Ball&quot;. 
* Black Box Recorder recorded a version in 1998, which appears on the US version of their album &quot;England Made Me&quot;.

